{"html":"<br/>\n<h2>Fact Symbols with Injective Instances</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\">Counter(id,&lt;)</p><br/>\n<h2>Multiset Rewriting Rules</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) isend:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !KU( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> K( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) irecv:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !KD( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) Create:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Fr( ~s ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> Start( ~s ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Counter( ~s, %1 ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) Inc:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( %x ), Counter( s, %x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> Number( %x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Counter( s, (%x%+%1) ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">// loop breaker: [1]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) AttackerMsg:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> Value( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) AttackerPub:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( $x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> PubValue( $x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) AttackerNat:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( x ), Counter( ~s, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> NatValue( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) InOut:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( %x ), In( (%x%+%1%+%1%+%1) ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> Out( &lt;(%x%+%1%+%1), %1, %1, %x, (%x%+%1), (%x%+%1)&gt; )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span></p><br/>\n","title":"Multiset rewriting rules and restrictions"}